captions.text:
-You should have seen her face, man. It was everywhere!
-Ha...your mum's awesome.
I have never seen this pub before.

Yeah, this is my favourite place!
CRAZIEST drinks!
Are you calling me a liar, sir?

No, the drink.
It's CALLED a 'Total Overreaction'.

[Chris coughs]
I just had a 'Pygmy Stallion'.

Oh, that's the 'Recurring Gag'.
I've had that before.

-Look, Tom, there's...a reason I brought you here toda--
-[gags]
-Stop drinking it!
I...have...no idea what you just said.

Nope. That's just the
'Recurring Gag' again.

Tom, look...I'm...
I'm trying to say that--

-Give me a 'Perpetual Motion' instead.
-Tom, look, I'm...I'm trying to tell you that...

Chris, I...I like my friends
like I like my Whisky.

-Let me guess: Straight!
-NOT TRYING TO SLEEP WITH ME.
Well, I need a 'More Understanding Friend.'
Why don't you give me a shot.
Could I get five 'Minutes to Think About It'.
Can I at least get a little 'Consideration'?
I don't see 'Us Working Out', so how about...

-...'Get Over It'
-Well I don't see a 'Future Without You', so...

Yeah, we're out of those
I'm afraid.
Can I at least get a 'Reluctant Compromise'?

Are you guys gonna drink
ANY of these?

Tom...can I at least get you
one more drink?

So that was a video which I made
to help fight cancer, weirdly enough.

So please watch the video over here
to unravel the mystery of

what that had to do with
cancer in any way.

This is a really bad shirt.
Why am I wearing this?
